      <div class="current-roles" id="current-roles">
          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_3731">
            <h1 id="director-general-financial-services">Director General, Financial Services</h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>Responsibilities include:</p>

<ul>
  <li>ensuring the delivery of HM Treasury’s work programme, in particular supporting the government’s objective to promote stability, fairness, efficiency and competitiveness in financial markets</li>
  <li>leading the Treasury’s relationships with the Prudential Regulatory Authority and the Financial Conduct Authority, and representing HM Treasury on the Bank of England’s Financial Policy Committee</li>
  <li>engaging with external stakeholders in the financial services industry, including consumer groups, industry groups and financial institutions</li>
</ul>
</div>
